data.description: Very aggressively priced for all this warm and cozy home has to offer! Enjoy prime living within this highly sought-after, gated Pulte Homes community! Lakewood Village is a small, quiet, safe, and SUPER neighborly community that's perfectly located in the heart of South Fort Myers. Ft Myers and Sanibel Beaches, Shopping, Dining, Schools and Churches are all within a short drive away. Our featured 3Bd/2.5Ba townhome offers a very private, and officially designated by Lee Co, 'Preserve' view. Glass Storm Door, Window Coverings, and Ceiling Fans throughout! AC new in 2018. Whether you’re looking through the huge 8’ tall triple-set of sliding doors from within this beautiful home, or sitting on your screened lanai enjoying the wonderful beauty SW Florida has to offer, you will be reminded every day that you are exactly where you have always wanted to be! Make an appointment and let me show you how much you are going to love this quiet little community I, too, have called home for nearly 19 years! I promise you will love it here! Come see!
